\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1.1}{\ignorespaces Dispersion relations of a 1D p-wave superconductor plotted at three different $\mu $ values. a) The trivial p-wave pairing scenario. The individual majorana particles each couple to the majorana on the same site. b) The critical value for $\mu $ where the gap closes. c) The topological p-wave pairing scenario. The majorana particles pair with majoranas on the nearest-neighbor site instead of on the same site. Two majorana zero modes are left on the edges of the wire, consistent with the bulk-boundary correspondence.}}{5}{figure.1.1}%
